MOST IMMEDIATE
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 7th July, 2021:
Shri D.V. Sadananda Gowda relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister
of Chemicals and Fertilizers.
SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 7th July, 2021
Shri Ravi Shankar Prasad relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of
Law and Justice; Minister of Communications; and Minister of Electronics and
Information Technology.
Shri Thaawar Chand Gehlot relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister
of Social Justice and Empowerment.

Dr. Harsh Vardhan relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of Health

Sciences.
Shri Prakash Javadekar relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of
Environment, Forest and Climate Change; Minister of Information and
Broadcasting; and Minister of Heavy Industries and Public Enterprises.

the Ministry of Environment, Forest and Climate Change.
Shri Dhotre Sanjay Shamrao relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister
of State in the Ministry of Education; Minister of State in the Ministry of
